{"tid":1715233,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"難道這就是封鎖互聯網的原因？","createTime":"2019-11-13T04:53:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T08:23:25.000Z","uid":30561,"like":25,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"623ae9bba4f5d9535c10ee73f07961e7d6ba25d4","tid":1715233,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T04:53:40.000Z","msg":"難道這就是封鎖互聯網的原因？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fWHpn0C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfWHpn0C.jpg&h=db18e38c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"030b4467f90c3fda6baf63ac421295bae3cad95a","tid":1715233,"uid":30561,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T04:54:18.000Z","msg":"他們知道的跟全世界都不一樣"},{"pid":"1af76f9203718cde96de0b1c0f119c6428b14dd9","tid":1715233,"uid":30561,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T04:54:50.000Z","msg":"奇異平行世界"},{"pid":"49febdc5f5a1a7d807f86cdf14ad1599c7b5085c","tid":1715233,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T04:56:16.000Z","msg":"邪惡到了極點"},{"pid":"093ce2bda0da521e46e86511014a2595eedb80ed","tid":1715233,"uid":46155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T04:56:21.000Z","msg":"world8964"},{"pid":"91704fe907e7b33750bfdf3edf8f894a9b9e07b0","tid":1715233,"uid":189564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T04:56:39.000Z","msg":"cls"},{"pid":"3032d87995db1696347cd3a0495aea29db1fd42f","tid":1715233,"uid":177485,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T04:56:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 平行世界"},{"pid":"79d91ef6922037a9f0b2232db7ab1f54446fed35","tid":1715233,"uid":224510,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T04:57:32.000Z","msg":"莫非何君係SuperHero<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5ec78dda1df90b87e4b7e87ec52b35f0f34beef","tid":1715233,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T04:57:58.000Z","msg":"中大經歷了一日一夜的激戰之後，市民都擔心校園內學生的安危，中大大學體育中心（U Gym）更用作臨時「戰地醫院」，處理逾百名傷者。教育局對香港學生安危視而不見，只是宣佈家長可視乎情況，決定子女是否上學，反而更關心身處中大校園內的內地學生，警方疑似派輪艇接走他們。<br />\n相關新聞：【抗暴之戰】傳中大內地生求救全被接走 海外生：未見佢哋離開宿舍<br />\n<br />\n從網上流傳的照片，今早大約10時，一群家長與學生聚集於在馬料水碼頭，所有家長都是說普通話。大批疑似內地學生一袋二袋，並拖住行李箱，經樟樹灘路往科學園方向到達碼頭，並登上一艘香港警察輪艇，疑似「着草」。有讀者更報料指，學生上船的時候，警察更會先詢問學生是否有內地的身分證。<br />\n此外，網上亦流傳有團體接走內地學生的訊息，「如果想要走，不要帶行李箱，帶一些重要的隨身東西」、「香島中學集合坐車去深圳」、「中聯辦的意思是，能走都走」。<br />\n相關新聞：【瘋警中大槍轟學生】沈旭暉斥如日軍解放軍屠殺：超齡紅衞兵病態報復<br />\n<br />\n近上午11時，《蘋果》記者在馬料水新舊碼頭附近，惟未見有人聚集，其中新碼頭只有一艘翠華渡輪船隻停泊，船上沒有人。而在橋下路的水警港外區總部，有兩艘小型水警輪停泊，基地內亦有警車、小型旅遊巴、私家車，但未見異樣。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191113/60261140?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2UULbTbzV-6sxIptfYE2UC70al0l82HrCa_wqc1S2v8AC6_BsrurzWS-Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191113%2F60261140%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2UULbTbzV-6sxIptfYE2UC70al0l82HrCa_wqc1S2v8AC6_BsrurzWS-Q&d=lZ7jQHZQyV3jEURUmMbLadmOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=f131819a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191113%2F60261140%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2UULbTbzV-6sxIptfYE2UC70al0l82HrCa_wqc1S2v8AC6_BsrurzWS-Q&h=d6a72b3c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191113/60261140?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2UULbTbzV-6sxIptfYE2UC70al0l82HrCa_wqc1S2v8AC6_BsrurzWS-Q</a>"},{"pid